{"tid":1426634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"克警已經進入路西法效應","createTime":"2019-08-07T03:14:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T06:37:00.000Z","uid":260089,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"083db7cb2f165238238b2a3ab7043fccb8a40f64","tid":1426634,"uid":260089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:14:05.000Z","msg":"為何平凡的普通人或社會團體，在特定情形之下會轉變成為他們原本所厭惡甚至是獵殺的事物，進而導致家庭、社會甚至是國家之混亂與動盪？菲利浦教授做出了以下解釋：<br />\n<br />\n1.首先，在有意或不經意之情形下跨越自己的道德底線。<br />\n<br />\n2.將其他人或個體去人性化。<br />\n<br />\n3.將自己去識別化。(透過匿名、變裝等方式、如：三K黨)<br />\n<br />\n4.分散與推諉個人之責任。(如：納粹)<br />\n<br />\n5.盲目服從於權威。<br />\n<br />\n6.不經批判地盲目服從團體規範。<br />\n<br />\n7.藉由不作為與冷漠，被動地容忍惡存在。<br />\n<br />\n至於如何克服這情形？菲利普&middot;津巴多教授表示：透過與那些為惡之人同樣的平凡人在日常生活中的平凡義舉，即可以對社會造成正面之影響"},{"pid":"36df8a1e463491819bda7ddd0a5c25531bc2a446","tid":1426634,"uid":260089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:14:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f77d64b65ea42946a4984c3e0c792e13b2c87c74","tid":1426634,"uid":260089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:14:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d6bf7fc37ec082185c49b60f08aca51b993b92e","tid":1426634,"uid":260089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:15:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b99547f60570412a1af15103aa152c7f139e1405","tid":1426634,"uid":19087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:16:06.000Z","msg":"巴打識嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ba9528b6cfac41dbe96acfbf993d83d4411099","tid":1426634,"uid":275901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:16:42.000Z","msg":"14年個陣已經係咁"},{"pid":"b18361ed817142af03941e888a475d98040f1938","tid":1426634,"uid":260089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b99547f60570412a1af15103aa152c7f139e1405","tid":1426634,"uid":19087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:16:06.000Z","msg":"巴打識嘢<img src=\"/assets